### Step 4 — Fix the SOW analyzer to return better milestone data

This is the real long-term fix. Go to Foundry → `sow-extractor-enterprise` → Schema → `milestones` field. The current description says extract verbatim. Change it to:

> Extract each milestone on a separate line in format: MILESTONE::<name> | DATE::<YYYY-MM-DD or TBD> | NOTES::<any notes>. One milestone per line. Do not concatenate multiple milestones onto one line.

Retrain. Then your parser will have clean structured input and the table will be perfect every time.

